title: Dream Brother - The videos of Jeff Buckley ISO
description:
This is a collection of official (and semi-official) videos from Jeff Buckley.
I made this as something to occupy myself with primarily, but as it 
turned out rather well, and as there&#039;s only proper &#039;bootleg&#039; DVDs available
in the trading circles, I thought I&#039;d share.

All video clips are of good quality (mostly DVD rips), though sadly the last clips (Classical 
festival with Alim Quasimov) are of poor quality, as the video was shot unprofessionally, 
and the lineage seems to be lengthy to say the least, yet they are very cool clips either way.


Tracklist:
Grace
Last Goodbye
So Real
Eternal Life
Everybody Here Wants You

The Way Young Lovers Do

What Will You Say (live with Alim Quasimov)
